strings: <Cap><leader> discovers a new recipe for the alchemy pot!
<Cap><string_1> <equal> <Cap><string_2> + <Cap><string_3>
<Cap><string_1> <equal> <Cap><string_2> + <Cap><string_3> + <Cap><string_4>

<se_high>*: Dig-dug, dig-dug, away with all the mud! ♪
We moles are clean, everything must gleam!
Dig-dug. Dig-dug. Dig-dug-dug! ♪
<se_high>*: What do you want!? Can't you see I'm busy!? Go away!

<se_high>*: I'm not here! Not here, I tell you!
And I didn't hear the boss summon us either.
<se_high>*: It's just too frightening. Dig-dig-dig...

<se_high>*: So what do you think of our hole!?
I bet humans couldn't build something like this!
<se_high>*: Moles are cool, see! Do you dig it!?

<se_high>*: You're a human, aren't you?
You must be pretty brave coming down here!

<se_high>*: Please help us! Put a stop to the boss!
Ever since he got hold of that harp,
it's been a nightmare!
<se_high>*: He's always had his moments, but this is getting ridiculous! He's been going at that harp every day since he got it!
<se_high>*: At this rate, we're all going to die of ear failure! Please! You have to stop him!

<se_high>*: ...Argh! I'm wearing earplugs, but
I can still feel its destructive power!
The boss is unstoppable!
<se_high>*: ...Argh! My earplugs are going to shatter into a million pieces! Go, boss...!

<se_high>*: We can't take it any more!
Somebody has to get that harp off him!

<se_high>*: We can't take any more of this!
If we have to put up with his music any longer,
we're all going to die!

There's no reply. Though he's still standing,
he seems to be unconscious.

<se_high>*: Apart from his terrible, awful music,
the boss is great. Huh...
<se_high>*: I hate them! I hate whoever it was that invented music! And I hate whoever told the boss about it even more!

<se_high>*: When the boss is back on his feet again,
we're going to leave this place and start again somewhere else.
<se_high>*: I can't believe you were able to take the boss's music at such close range! And I never imagined anyone could beat him...

<se_high>*: You humans aren't bad.
But you still can't dig a hole like us moles!

<se_high>*: Thanks for putting a stop to the boss.
Now our ears can finally have a rest.
<se_high>*: Hey! What do you think you're doing with the boss!? Huh!
<se_high>*: Yikes! Humans are pretty scary if they can defeat someone as great as Don Mole! Dig-dig-dig...

<se_high>*: The boss isn't too badly injured.
He'll pull through, anyway.
Thanks for taking it easy on him.

<se_high>*: Boss!? Stay with it!
Oh no, not that song again...

<se_high>*: It's okay! We don't need to hear it again!
Just stay with it, boss!

<se_low>*: Urgh... Would ya dug it...
Done beat by humans...
<se_low>*: But what's done's done... Hah... That harp, though... I'd have topped the charts for years to come with that baby!

<se_high>*: This isn't a bad place as places go.
Rent's a bit high, mind.
<se_high>*: Hey! You! This is mine! I was here first!
